	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you're looking for Bible verses for kids, you're in the right place.</strong> Every child needs to know one big thing: God made you, He knows your name, and He loves you no matter what. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh, easy-to-read English Bible you can read <em>and listen to</em> together for free — and it shows God as a loving <em>Father</em> on every page. Whether you searched "Bible verses for kids," "short Bible verses for kids to memorize," verses for children, or "God loves me," the answer is the same and it's simple: you have a good, good Father in heaven who is always near. Younger ones can also visit our <a href="/bible-for/children/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Bible verses for children</a> page.`}
