	painsBodyHtml={`<p>Every child carries a little heart that feels a lot — happy and scared, brave and shy, all in the same day. When kids are afraid or feel left out or have big, big feelings, what they need most is to know they are safe and loved.</p><p>That's why telling kids about God's love early matters so much. A child who learns young that God made them, knows their name, and loves them no matter what carries that truth for the rest of their life. There is a good, good Father in heaven, and He has something gentle to say to every child.</p>`}
