	aFatherHeading={`A Father for kids`}
	aFatherBodyHtml={`<p>Here is the most important thing a child can ever hear: you have a <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">Father</strong> in heaven who made you on purpose and loves you with all His heart. He is a good, good Father.</p><p>He knows your name. He knows how many hairs are on your head. He sees you when you're happy and when you're sad and when you're scared in the dark. And He is right there with you, every minute, because He is always near.</p><p>You don't have to be the biggest or the best or get everything right. God loves you no matter what — when you win and when you mess up, when you're brave and when you're afraid. Nothing you do could ever make Him love you less. You are His child, and He is so glad you're His.</p>`}
