		{ question: `What are short Bible verses for kids to memorize?`, answer: `Short verses are easiest for little ones to learn by heart. Try Psalm 56:3 ("When I am afraid, I trust in You"), 1 John 4:19 ("We love because He loved us first"), Psalm 23:1 ("The Lord is my shepherd"), and Joshua 1:9 ("Be strong and brave… God is with you"). Read them together a few times, then say them out loud at bedtime. You can hear the audio free at fathersheartbible.com/read.` },
